{% block bodyContent %}

  <h2>January 2020</h2>

  <table class="nhsuk-table">
    <caption class="nhsuk-table__caption">Updates to the service manual in January 2020</caption>
    <thead class="nhsuk-table__head">
      <tr class="nhsuk-table__row">
        <th class="nhsuk-table__header" scope="col" style="width: 25%;">Section</th>
        <th class="nhsuk-table__header" scope="col">Update</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody class="nhsuk-table__body">
      <tr class="nhsuk-table__row">
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell">Content style guide</td>
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell"><p>Added new entries for "<a href="/content/a-to-z-of-nhs-health-writing#chronic">chronic</a>", "<a href="/content/a-to-z-of-nhs-health-writing#acute">acute</a>", "<a href="/content/a-to-z-of-nhs-health-writing#renal">renal</a>" and "<a href="/content/a-to-z-of-nhs-health-writing#kidney">kidney</a>" to the <a href="/content/a-to-z-of-nhs-health-writing">A to Z of NHS health writing</a></p></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="nhsuk-table__row">
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell">Content style guide</td>
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell"><p>Amended index page and side navigation of <a href="/content/how-to-write-good-questions-for-forms">How to write good questions</a> to improve search results</p></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="nhsuk-table__row">
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell">Terms and conditions</td>
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell"><p>Updated <a href="/terms-and-conditions">Terms and conditions</a> page to make it clear the service manual is covered by the Open Government Licence</p></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="nhsuk-table__row">
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell">Privacy</td>
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell"><p>Amended <a href="/your-privacy">Your privacy</a> page to reflect service manual policy and practice</p></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="nhsuk-table__row">
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell">Cookies</td>
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell"><p>Updated <a href="">cookies page</a> to reflect current cookies practice and let people opt in</p></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="nhsuk-table__row">
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell">Service standard</td>
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell"><p>Amended <a href="/service-standard">NHS service standard</a> page and <a href="/service-standard/about">About the NHS service standard</a> page to make it clear that teams working to the GOV.UK service standard must meet all 14 points</p></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="nhsuk-table__row">
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell">Content style guide</td>
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell"><p>Made it easier for people to understand negative <a href="/content/formatting-and-punctuation#contractions">contractions</a>. Added "<a href="/content/a-to-z-of-nhs-health-writing#can't-or-cannot">can't or cannot</a>" and "<a href="/content/a-to-z-of-nhs-health-writing#don't-or-do-not">don't or do not</a>" to the A to Z of NHS health writing</p></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="nhsuk-table__row">
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell">Get in touch</td>
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell"><p>Added 'Need help?' or 'Get in touch' details to pages across the site</p></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="nhsuk-table__row">
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell">Components</td>
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell"><p>Added a <a href="/design-system/components/hint-text">hint text</a> page to components after user research showed users did not find hint text under text input and similar components</p></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="nhsuk-table__row">
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell">Community</td>
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell"><p>Added new page: <a href="/community/backlog-of-components-and-patterns">Backlog of components and patterns</a></p></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="nhsuk-table__row">
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell">What's new</td>
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell"><p>Added <a href="/whats-new">What's new</a> section with updates and blog pages</p></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="nhsuk-table__row">
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell">Content style guide</td>
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell"><p>Updated the <a href="/content/inclusive-language">inclusive language page</a> with revised guidance on "sex, gender and sexuality", "race, ethnicity, religion and nationality" and "age"</p></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="nhsuk-table__row">
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell">Content style guide</td>
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell"><p>Updated the <a href="/content/a-to-z-of-nhs-health-writing"> A to Z of NHS health writing</a> with entries on "<a href="/content/a-to-z-of-nhs-health-writing#pharmacy">pharmacy</a>", "<a href="/content/a-to-z-of-nhs-health-writing#chemist">chemist</a>" and "<a href="/content/a-to-z-of-nhs-health-writing#sex-assigned-or-registered-at-birth">sex assigned or registered at birth</a>"</p></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="nhsuk-table__row">
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell">Service standard</td>
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell"><p>Updated <a href="/service-standard/17-make-your-service-interoperable">section 17 of the service standard</a> with more detail about interoperability standards</p></td>
      </tr>
       <tr class="nhsuk-table__row">
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell">Content style guide</td>
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell"><p>Amended the guidance on using the number 1 on the <a href="/content/numbers-measurements-dates-time">numbers, measurements, dates and time page</a></p></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

